{"type": "article", "id": 25239, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-11T06:59:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 26037, "name": "The Twig Co."}, {"id": 26038, "name": "Diesel Living"}, {"id": 26039, "name": "Seletti"}, {"id": 26040, "name": "Enserio Studio"}, {"id": 26041, "name": "Danny Kuo"}, {"id": 26042, "name": "Ali Safa A"}, {"id": 26043, "name": "Matt Lee"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123758BFeNxwqU8z5WnbfH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>Staircase by Danny Kuo</h2>\n<p>这个立柜兼有楼梯的功能，它由 9 个抽屉盒构成，最下面三个可以拉出来构成台阶。设计师想要节约空间而设计了这个有 2.6 米高的柜子，但同时高度也带来了新的不方便，因而产生了楼梯的设计。他还有一个柜子将抽屉换成了开放的格子，设计原理相同，也都给生活带来了灵活和变化。设计师 Danny Kuo 是出生在荷兰的华人，目前在上海工作，<a href=\"http://www.dannykuo.com/index.html\">这里是他的主页</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190219WkhldS5syAVu0Fon.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75451264\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190219IojbFdVHOGkQypgR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190220m7hZgk90o35e8I6u.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50234742\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190221YilauCqJkz3DxGtp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50234742\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190222NZrX4Pi9TqBdzJmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Kyoto Stool by The Twig Co.</h2>\n<p>这个方形的小家具即可以做边桌也可以做凳子，日本设计团队 The Twig Co.从树中获得灵感，将支撑结构设计成树干的形式，有一个较粗的主干和两个细分支连接座位和地面，构成了一种平衡。设计团队认为树连接了天堂和地面，而它的自然特征也带来了一种温和的居家气氛。售价 175 美元，<a href=\"http://twigcreative.myshopify.com/products/kyoto\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190222yW1letEK48niL2ub.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071902228IodzSRkDHGCa4b3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190223Ss64xDUH1tZVRd7w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071902249n8LfI3SuXPcFTj5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190224xziWaDhMK2qYPR4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Femton by Ali Safa A</h2>\n<p>这组小型健身物品是由橡木和大理石制作的，包括哑铃、跳绳等可以在家中使用的器械。瑞典的工业设计学生 Ali Safa A 认为这些传统的器械并没有太多美观可言，因而统一用橡木和大理石设计，能与家庭中的家具搭配，也可作为装饰，让你在看到它的时候就能想起来运动。哑铃最大可达到 8.3 kg，<a href=\"http://analogueways.com/femton/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071902243F0CoRexdlO6hVgi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190225CnR5bYApU8yHhrGN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190226omLcZBvdVUDK91rG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190226YvjlLaGo9w37D2AN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190227cyNUarDb3AXhFqCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cosmic Diner by Diesel Living &amp; Seletti</h2>\n<p>这组餐具系列都带有一些好玩的科幻色彩，来自意大利家居品牌 Diesel Living 和意大利设计品牌 Seletti。餐盘的图案来自星球，而胡椒瓶则是一艘火箭，白色瓷盘的边缘是齿轮的形状，点缀以金属色提亮，在奇幻中富有想象力。这套餐具将和之前的系列一起在 2016 年米兰家居展上展出，<a href=\"http://store.diesel.com/magazine/en/living-category/home-accessories/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190227laDIB2oWw5eYUtS7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190228YDx5PWZ6pMR473zA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190228aKBsCLDTgR4Ft2kz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190229YufW2StTOerKnXIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071902294OFGlcJixVZy7zuW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70870871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Death Landscapes III by Matt Lee</h2>\n<p>英国视觉设计师 Matt Lee 用纸片做了这组浮雕作品。他用了同样颜色的纸张以不同形状相互叠加或相错，拼出了有浮雕效果的图案。可以看到纸张之间的凹凸纹路，在光影照射下形成了浅浅的阴影，很有层次。图案看起来有点抽象实则非常细腻，<a href=\"http://www.matt-lee.com/death-landscapes-3\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190230R9IcyuHazoxt6Xh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190231EnKMDbSiFlLh7PRV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190231rob7txnhXIWDqYCp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071902313C8vO9LAk0gslEyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190232IiTSL1DXMKUesCdP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cuarentona packaging by Enserio Studio</h2>\n<p>这款酒的包装外加了一层黑色的丝网，就增加了一层年轻和现代的色彩。酒瓶上的包装也采用黑白搭配的形式，依然可以透过菱形网格看到 Cuarentona 的名字，简洁时尚。这种来自西班牙的饮料加入了草药、香料以及经过 40 天干燥的甜茴香，所以在木质瓶盖上写出了 +40 的标注。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060719023290zyhmqXg5kd7vTW.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24814815\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190234fOt3DhZHjecT60uQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190235P7ul9LaH2SMfdbvc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190235JGiyUfVqXpD5ESk7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66527778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190236nv6ltV2N0KwZXOSz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}